Third Department,

March, 1983

(March 1, 1983) In the Matter of the Application of Robert L. Miller for Reinstatement as an Attorney.

—■ Application for reinstatement granted and petitioner, Robert L. Miller, reinstated as an attorney and counselor at law effective immediately. Order entered. Mahoney, P. J., Sweeney, Kane, Main and Weiss, JJ., concur.
